headline: Analog Devices Governance Debate Puts Special Meeting Rights In Focus
summary: Analog Devices (NasdaqGS:ADI) is facing shareholder activism focused on special meeting rights. The company is actively engaging with investors on voting rights, transparency, and its approach to board accountability. Analog Devices develops analog, mixed signal, and digital signal processing technologies that sit at the core of many industrial, communications, and automotive...
